{"comments":"Trigger Types — Conditions that start/stop effects\n\nTriggers are pure predicates evaluated against FrameState.\nNo side effects. No callbacks. Just data.\n\n## Trigger Categories\n\n- **Mouse**: hover, enter, leave, down, up, dragging, idle, region\n- **Keyboard**: key down, up, held, modifier active\n- **Focus**: gained, lost, within, visible\n- **Time**: delay, timestamp, interval, frame count, elapsed range\n- **Scroll**: position, progress, direction, velocity\n- **Viewport**: width, height, visible, orientation\n- **Animation**: progress range, complete, phase, spring at rest\n\n## Composition\n\nTriggers compose with boolean algebra via TriggerCombinator:\n- `TriggerAnd`: Both must be true\n- `TriggerOr`: Either must be true\n- `TriggerNot`: Negation\n- `TriggerXor`: Exactly one true\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","EffectEvent","Trigger"],"MouseTrigger"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[81,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/EffectEvent/Trigger.purs","start":[81,3]},"title":"TriggerMouse"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","EffectEvent","Trigger"],"KeyboardTrigger"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[82,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/EffectEvent/Trigger.purs","start":[82,3]},"title":"TriggerKeyboard"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","EffectEvent","Trigger"],"FocusTrigger"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[83,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/EffectEvent/Trigger.purs","start":[83,3]},"title":"TriggerFocus"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","EffectEvent","Trigger"],"TimeTrigger"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"en